name: Henri Rousseau | Hypernetwork
description:
Hypernetwork based on a selection of high quality images of Henri Rousseau's work. Rousseau was a French post-impressionist painter known for his vivid jungle scenes.

While this doesn't mirror his style precisely, which would be hard for any neural network to do, it does create some really stylish looking foliage. 0.75 strength seems to yield the best results.

This is a SD v1.5 model trained on v1-5-pruned-emaonly.ckpt.
